    rdfs:comment "Moreau's Chimera converts the threatening hybrid into an object of desire: winged and human above, bestial below, she fuses the ascensional pull of flight with a nyctomorphic undertow of obscurity and seduction, where fire and fang no longer signal attack but the dark, submerged allure of the abyss itself."@en ;
