beastiary:ability_accumulate_treasures a beast:Ability ;
    rdfs:label "Treasure hoarding"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "The behavioral tendency to collect and guard valuable objects such as gold or precious stones."@en,
        "Trolls tend to accumulate treasures because they are attracted to the materiality of things. It represents a declination of Durand's mystical structures that focus on sensory attachment."@en ;
    beast:belongsToImaginaryStructure beast:MysticalStructure ;
    beast:isGovernedBy beast:NocturnalRegime .

beastiary:ability_deadly_scream a beast:Ability ;
    rdfs:label "Deadly scream"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A vocalization so powerful it causes death or severe harm to those who hear it."@en,
        "The lethal cry is formless sonic terror erupting from the unknown, enacting the nyctomorphic voracity of night that dissolves the listener into the abyss."@en ;
    beast:belongsToImaginaryStructure beast:SchizomorphicStructure ;
    beast:embodiesImaginarySymbol beast:NyctomorphicSymbol ;
    beast:isGovernedBy beast:DiurnalRegime .

beastiary:ability_killing_gaze a beast:Ability ;
    rdfs:label "Killing gaze"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A lethal power transmitted invisibly through the eyes, without weapon or bite, belongs to the nyctomorphic register: death arrives as formless, unseeable agency, the abyss looking back rather than a jaw striking."@en,
        "The ability to cause instant death through direct eye contact, distinct from petrification."@en ;
    beast:belongsToImaginaryStructure beast:SchizomorphicStructure ;
    beast:embodiesImaginarySymbol beast:NyctomorphicSymbol ;
    beast:isGovernedBy beast:DiurnalRegime .

beastiary:ability_petrifying_gaze a beast:Ability ;
    rdfs:label "Petrifying gaze"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "The ability to turn living beings to stone through direct eye contact."@en,
        "Turning living flesh to stone is the catamorphic degradation of flesh: the body fixed, fallen, and hardened out of life."@en ;
    beast:belongsToImaginaryStructure beast:SchizomorphicStructure ;
    beast:embodiesImaginarySymbol beast:CatamorphicSymbol ;
    beast:isGovernedBy beast:DiurnalRegime .

