    rdfs:label "Venomous"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Aggressive natural weaponry expresses the teriomorphic 'enemy symbol' of feral chaos and the bestial threat of the striking attack."@en,
        "The creature produces or secretes a toxic substance capable of harming or killing through bite, touch, or breath."@en ;
